@startuml assessment-lifecycle
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam stateBackgroundColor #F0EEF8
skinparam stateBorderColor #3D108A
skinparam stateArrowColor #2E2E38
skinparam stateFontSize 13
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E8F8F8
skinparam noteBorderColor #27ACAA
skinparam noteFontSize 12

[*] --> Idle : session created

Idle --> InProgress : setAnswer or skipIndicator\n(first indicator answered)

InProgress --> InProgress : setAnswer, setEvidence,\nskipIndicator (more indicators)

InProgress --> Complete : all 47 indicators answered\nor validly skipped\n[isAssessmentComplete()]

Complete --> InProgress : setAnswer(null)\n(an indicator cleared)

state "Unlocked Screens" as Unlocked {
  state "Results" as Res
  state "Gap Analysis" as Gap
  state "Compliance" as Comp
}

Complete --> Unlocked : completion gate opens\n(RequireComplete allows\n/results, /gap-analysis,\n/compliance)

Unlocked --> Complete : return to assessment

Complete --> Idle : resetAll()
InProgress --> Idle : resetAll()
Unlocked --> Idle : resetAll()

note right of InProgress
  Completion gate is closed.
  RequireComplete redirects
  /results, /gap-analysis and
  /compliance back to
  /assessment.
  13 BCT indicators cannot
  be skipped; per dimension
  at most floor(0.20 x n)
  skips are allowed.
end note

note bottom of Unlocked
  Reached only when every
  dimension is complete.
  Screens read the scoring
  selectors from the store.
end note

@enduml
